ods beginning on or after 1 April 2018. Application of Ind AS 115 does not have any material impact on the financial statements of the Company.  n  n4.Provision for taxes, employee benefits and other provisions for contingencies have been considered on estimated basis.  n  n5.The above statement of financial results has been reviewed by the Audit Committee and has been approved by the Board of Directors in their respective meetings held on 31st January, 2019.  n  n6.As required under regulation 33 of SEBI (Listing Obligations and Disclosure Requirements) Regulations 2015, the Statutory Auditors have conducted a limited review of the above financial results for the quarter and nine months ended 31st December, 2018.  n  n7.Previous period figures have been regrouped / rearranged wherever necessary.  n </in-bse-fin:DisclosureOfNotesOnFinancialResultsExplanatoryTextBlock>
